Note on third-party data:

Refinitiv Tick History intraday data (RICs ESc1, TYc1, FGBLc1, STXE, FFc1-3,
FEIc1-4, SRc1-2) are NOT covered by this license and are NOT redistributed in
this repository. Reproduction requires user's own subscription via WRDS or
Refinitiv. See README.md and docs/data_metodologia.md.

Third-party datasets included for academic replication (under their respective
licenses):
  - Altavilla et al. (2019) EA-MPD database (academic replication)
  - Jarocinski-Karadi MP surprises (academic replication)
  - FRED snapshots (US public domain)
